all different kinds of cells.

01:24:12.380 --> 01:24:15.450
One type, called
mechanoreceptors,

01:24:15.450 --> 01:24:19.920
sense forces of movement or
pressure applied to the tooth.

01:24:19.920 --> 01:24:23.190
