01:24:56.780 --> 01:25:00.530
Another type of cell called an
osteoblast comes in and then

01:25:00.530 --> 01:25:03.990
builds up the jaw bone so
the PDL cushion can get back

01:25:03.990 --> 01:25:08.770
to its proper shape holding
the tooth in its new position.

